msgid "# Slash Commands"
msgstr "# 斜杠命令"

msgid ""
"vLLM Ascend supports slash commands in pull request comments to trigger CI "
"workflows. See the [Permission](#permission) section for who can trigger "
"each command."
msgstr ""
"vLLM Ascend 支持在拉取请求评论中使用斜杠命令来触发 CI 工作流。有关谁可以触发每个命令，请参阅[权限](#permission)部分。"

msgid "## Available Commands"
msgstr "## 可用命令"

msgid "### `/e2e`"
msgstr "### `/e2e`"

msgid ""
"Run specific E2E tests under `tests/e2e/pull_request/`. Tests are "
"automatically routed to the appropriate NPU runner based on the test path."
msgstr "运行 `tests/e2e/pull_request/` 下的特定 E2E 测试。测试会根据路径自动路由到相应的 NPU 运行器。"

msgid "**Routing rules** (matched in order):"
msgstr "**路由规则**（按顺序匹配）："

msgid ""
"| Test path contains | Runner |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `four_card/_310p` | 310P 4-card |\n"
"| `_310p` (under `one_card`/`two_card`) | 310P single card |\n"
"| `four_card` | A3 4-card |\n"
"| `two_card` | A3 2-card |\n"
"| Others (e.g. `one_card`) | A2 single card |"
msgstr ""
"| 测试路径包含 | 运行器 |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `four_card/_310p` | 310P 4卡 |\n"
"| `_310p`（位于 `one_card`/`two_card` 下） | 310P 单卡 |\n"
"| `four_card` | A3 4卡 |\n"
"| `two_card` | A3 2卡 |\n"
"| 其他（例如 `one_card`） | A2 单卡 |"

msgid ""
"> Only test paths under `tests/e2e/pull_request/` are supported. Tests in "
"`tests/e2e/nightly/`, `tests/e2e/models/`, or `tests/e2e/doctests/` are not "
"accepted by `/e2e`. Use `/nightly` for nightly tests."
msgstr ""
"> 仅支持 `tests/e2e/pull_request/` 下的测试路径。`/e2e` 不接受 "
"`tests/e2e/nightly/`、`tests/e2e/models/` 或 `tests/e2e/doctests/` 中的测试。对于 "
"nightly 测试，请使用 `/nightly`。"

msgid ""
"Tests are run against both the community vLLM version and the latest "
"release."
msgstr "测试会针对社区 vLLM 版本和最新发布版本运行。"

msgid "### `/nightly`"
msgstr "### `/nightly`"

msgid ""
"Trigger specific nightly test cases on A2 and A3. Supports only PR comments."
" Test case names correspond to the `test_config.name` entries defined in "
"`schedule_nightly_test_a2.yaml` and `schedule_nightly_test_a3.yaml`."
msgstr ""
"在 A2 和 A3 上触发特定的 nightly 测试用例。仅支持 PR 评论。测试用例名称对应于 "
"`schedule_nightly_test_a2.yaml` 和 `schedule_nightly_test_a3.yaml` 中定义的 "
"`test_config.name` 条目。"

msgid ""
"| Syntax | Scope |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases>` | Runs on `main` branch |\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases> --branch <branch>` | Runs on the specified branch |\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases> --aop_enabled` | Enable AOP hooks (bisect / classify) on failure |"
msgstr ""
"| 语法 | 范围 |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases>` | 在 `main` 分支上运行 |\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases> --branch <branch>` | 在指定分支上运行 |\n"
"| `/nightly <test_cases> --aop_enabled` | 在失败时启用 AOP 钩子（二分查找/分类） |"

msgid ""
"Use `--branch <name>` to specify a target branch. Without `--branch`, all "
"arguments are treated as test cases (separated by commas or spaces) and the "
"branch defaults to `main`."
msgstr ""
"使用 `--branch <name>` 指定目标分支。如果不使用 `--branch`，所有参数都被视为测试用例（以逗号或空格分隔），分支默认为 "
"`main`。"

msgid ""
"Use `--aop_enabled` to enable the AOP (Aspect-Oriented Programming) pipeline, which\n"
"automatically captures test results, classifies failures (env vs. code), and triggers\n"
"binary bisect for genuine failures. By default, AOP hooks are disabled."
msgstr ""
"使用 `--aop_enabled` 启用 AOP（面向切面编程）流水线，该流水线会自动捕获测试结果、\n"
"对失败进行分类（环境问题 vs 代码问题），并对真正的失败触发二分查找。\n"
"默认情况下，AOP 钩子是禁用的。"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: When commenting on a PR, the tests run on the PR branch "
"automatically in the triggered workflow; the `--branch` flag is primarily "
"used in issue comments."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：在对 PR 进行评论时，测试会在触发的工作流中自动在 PR 分支上运行；`--branch` 标志主要用于 issue 评论。"

msgid "**Common test case names (A2):**"
msgstr "**常见测试用例名称（A2）：**"

msgid ""
"`test_custom_op`, `test_custom_op_multi_card`, `qwen3-vl-32b-instruct-w8a8`,"
" `qwen3-32b-int8`, `MiniMax-M2.5-w8a8-QuaRot-A2`, `Qwen3.5-27B-w8a8-A2`, "
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w4a8-mtp`, `accuracy-group`"
msgstr ""
"`test_custom_op`, `test_custom_op_multi_card`, `qwen3-vl-32b-instruct-w8a8`,"
" `qwen3-32b-int8`, `MiniMax-M2.5-w8a8-QuaRot-A2`, `Qwen3.5-27B-w8a8-A2`, "
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w4a8-mtp`, `accuracy-group`"

msgid "**Common test case names (A3):**"
msgstr "**常见测试用例名称（A3）：**"

msgid ""
"`multi-node-deepseek-v3.2-W8A8-EP`, `mtpx-deepseek-r1-0528-w8a8`, "
"`deepseek-r1-0528-w8a8`, `kimi-k2-thinking`, "
"`qwen3-vl-235b-a22b-instruct-w8a8`, `custom-multi-ops`, ..."
msgstr ""
"`multi-node-deepseek-v3.2-W8A8-EP`, `mtpx-deepseek-r1-0528-w8a8`, "
"`deepseek-r1-0528-w8a8`, `kimi-k2-thinking`, "
"`qwen3-vl-235b-a22b-instruct-w8a8`, `custom-multi-ops`, ..."

msgid ""
"This triggers `workflow_dispatch` on both `schedule_nightly_test_a2.yaml` "
"and `schedule_nightly_test_a3.yaml`."
msgstr ""
"这会在 `schedule_nightly_test_a2.yaml` 和 `schedule_nightly_test_a3.yaml` 上触发 "
"`workflow_dispatch`。"

msgid "### `/cherry-pick`"
msgstr "### `/cherry-pick`"

msgid ""
"Cherry-pick a PR's commits onto a specified target branch and create a new "
"PR. This is useful for backporting fixes to release branches."
msgstr "将一个 PR 的提交 cherry-pick 到指定的目标分支并创建一个新的 PR。这对于将修复反向移植到发布分支非常有用。"

msgid ""
"| Syntax | Description |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/cherry-pick <target_branch>` | Cherry-pick onto the specified branch |"
msgstr ""
"| 语法 | 描述 |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/cherry-pick <target_branch>` | Cherry-pick 到指定分支 |"

msgid ""
"A new PR will be created with the title format `[Cherry-pick] "
"<original_title> (from #<PR_NUMBER>)` and a body linking back to the "
"original PR."
msgstr ""
"将创建一个新 PR，标题格式为 `[Cherry-pick] <original_title> (from "
"#<PR_NUMBER>)`，正文包含指向原始 PR 的链接。"

msgid ""
"If the cherry-pick encounters merge conflicts, the command will report the "
"failure and the cherry-pick must be done manually."
msgstr "如果 cherry-pick 遇到合并冲突，该命令将报告失败，并且必须手动执行 cherry-pick。"

msgid "### `/revert`"
msgstr "### `/revert`"

msgid ""
"Revert a merged PR by creating a new PR that reverses its changes. The "
"revert targets the same base branch the original PR was merged into."
msgstr "通过创建一个新 PR 来撤销已合并 PR 的更改。回退的目标是原始 PR 合并到的同一个基础分支。"

msgid ""
"| Syntax | Description |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/revert` | Revert this PR (no arguments needed) |"
msgstr ""
"| 语法 | 描述 |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/revert` | 回退此 PR（无需参数） |"

msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

msgid ""
"A new PR will be created with the title format `[Revert] Revert "
"\"original_title\" (#PR_NUMBER)` and a body linking back to the original PR "
"and its merge commit."
msgstr ""
"将创建一个新 PR，标题格式为 `[Revert] Revert \"original_title\" (#PR_NUMBER)`，正文包含指向原始 "
"PR 及其合并提交的链接。"

msgid ""
"Only merged PRs can be reverted. If the revert encounters merge conflicts "
"(e.g., because the base branch has diverged significantly), the command will"
" report the failure and the revert must be done manually."
msgstr "只有已合并的 PR 才能被回退。如果回退遇到合并冲突（例如，因为基础分支已经严重偏离），该命令将报告失败，并且必须手动执行回退。"

msgid "### `/rerun`"
msgstr "### `/rerun`"

msgid ""
"Re-run all failed workflow runs on the current PR commit. Useful when CI "
"jobs failed due to infrastructure issues."
msgstr "重新运行当前 PR 提交上所有失败的工作流运行。当 CI 作业因基础设施问题而失败时非常有用。"

msgid "## Behavior"
msgstr "## 行为"

msgid ""
"1. When you comment a slash command, a 👀 reaction is added to your comment to indicate it has been received\n"
"2. The corresponding CI workflow is triggered asynchronously\n"
"3. Upon completion, a 🎉 reaction and a summary comment are added"
msgstr ""
"1. 当你评论一个斜杠命令时，你的评论会添加一个 👀 反应，表示已收到\n"
"2. 相应的 CI 工作流会被异步触发\n"
"3. 完成后，会添加一个 🎉 反应和一条摘要评论"

msgid "## Scope"
msgstr "## 范围"

msgid ""
"| Command | PR comments | Issue comments |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| `/e2e` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/rerun` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/cherry-pick` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/revert` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/nightly` | ✅ | ❌ |"
msgstr ""
"| 命令 | PR 评论 | Issue 评论 |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| `/e2e` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/rerun` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/cherry-pick` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/revert` | ✅ | ❌ |\n"
"| `/nightly` | ✅ | ❌ |"

msgid "## Permission"
msgstr "## 权限"

msgid ""
"| Command | Who can trigger |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/e2e` | PR author, or users with triage+ permission on the repository |\n"
"| `/rerun` | PR author, or users with triage+ permission on the repository |\n"
"| `/cherry-pick` | PR author, or users with triage+ permission on the repository |\n"
"| `/revert` | PR author, or users with triage+ permission on the repository |\n"
"| `/nightly` | Users with triage+ permission on the repository only |"
msgstr ""
"| 命令 | 谁可以触发 |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| `/e2e` | PR 作者，或具有仓库 triage+ 权限的用户 |\n"
"| `/rerun` | PR 作者，或具有仓库 triage+ 权限的用户 |\n"
"| `/cherry-pick` | PR 作者，或具有仓库 triage+ 权限的用户 |\n"
"| `/revert` | PR 作者，或具有仓库 triage+ 权限的用户 |\n"
"| `/nightly` | 仅限具有仓库 triage+ 权限的用户 |"

msgid ""
"Permission is verified via the GitHub API "
"(`repos/{owner}/{repo}/collaborators/{user}/permission`)."
msgstr ""
"权限通过 GitHub API (`repos/{owner}/{repo}/collaborators/{user}/permission`) "
"进行验证。"

msgid "**Usage:**"
msgstr "**用法：**"

msgid "**Examples:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"
